<section id="camp">
  <div>
    <h3>[Girls & Boys Grade 2-12] South 2014 volleyball camp</h3>
    <p>
      <span class="label label-important">Registration open!</span>
      Registration is now open for <%= link_to "South's Summer Volleyball Camp", summer_camp_flyer_url, :target => '_blank' %>. 
      Work on skills with South's volleyball staff and prepare for fall volleyball season. 
      New this year, summer camp is open to boys! As always, any player may register for camp, regardless of residence or attendance area. 
    </p>
    <p>
      Three sessions are offered for girls Youth (grade 2-6), Middle School (grade 6-8), and High School (grade 9-12) players. 
      To register, or for more information about session times and pricing, download the camp 
      <%= link_to 'registration form', summer_camp_flyer_url, :target => '_blank' %>.
      Questions? 
      Contact <%= mail_to 'willingham@lakevillejuniors.com', 'Stephen Willingham', :encode => 'hex' %> or call 952-431-6341. 
    </p>  
  </div>
</section>

